# COMPONENT

## SimpleEntityViewSample

### PACKAGE

org.sample.simpleentityview

### DESCRIPTION

SimpleEntity-based view sample component.

### SPECIFICATION

This component demonstrates that the default generated `ENTITY > VIEW` read surface still works
when the source entity inherits common fields from `SimpleEntity`.

# ENTITY

## SimpleEntity

### DESCRIPTION

Common base entity that provides the standard inherited field set.

### KIND

simpleentity

# ENTITY

## Person

### EXTENDS

SimpleEntity

### DESCRIPTION

Concrete entity that adds `city` on top of the inherited `SimpleEntity` fields.

### ATTRIBUTE

| name  | type   | multiplicity |
|-------+--------+--------------|
| city  | string | 1            |

### VIEW

#### DESCRIPTION

The default generated `view` service is enough for this line.
